title: New: East – Old Age
body:
Australia on point for the millionth time this year.

**East** is a relatively new artist from New South Wales, and aside from that, there’s not a huge amount of information, however believe me when I say, this is STACKED with potential. Her debut track, _Old Age_, just feels like it deserves to be blasted out at festivals all round the world. With a hook that CHVRCHES would kill for, and like Foxes but with more angst and personality, I’m on my tenth listen and head over heels in love. Check out _Old Age_ below.
